<li><b>Walkthrough (90s)</b> — Executive Brief (KPIs, Key SLA Commitments), Top Risks (evidence), SLA Risk Assessment, Commercial Impact, Legends/Limitations.</li>
<li><b>Trust &amp; reproducibility (40s)</b> — same contract &rarr; same result; audit log; injection defense.</li>
<li><b>Close (20s)</b> — from contract to decision, safely, in minutes.</li>
</ol>
